{"id":19036,"date":"2024-01-10T20:54:20","date_gmt":"2021-02-10T15:24:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=19036"},"modified":"2022-06-27T11:25:25","modified_gmt":"2022-06-27T05:55:25","slug":"cove-lighting","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/cove-lighting\/","title":{"rendered":"Glowy And Gorgeous: Cove Lighting Ideas For Your Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\r\n<p><em>Light up your space in style now!<\/em><\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Lights are essential for every kind of home. Whether you are thinking from the point of view of aesthetics or overall functionality, lights add more character to your home. These days, many homeowners have recognised the value of selecting just the right lights for their homes. Cove lighting especially has become popular for the right reasons. Cove lighting designs not only transform the vibe of a room but also integrate well and take up less space.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Most importantly, if you have been a lover of warm and soft lights, then we cannot recommend false ceiling cove light designs enough. These lights effortlessly grant a glow to your space and serve as an indirect source of lighting. Moreover, they appear diffused and muted overall. The best thing about cove lighting is also that you can include them easily in your ceiling design and they are easy to maintain.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Got false ceilings at your home? Then cove lighting will seamlessly fit in. Though it is a simple technique of lighting, cove lights are preferred for the visual edge that they grant to the spaces. If you wish to have soft, diffused illumination across your living room, hallways, porch or even bedroom, then cove lighting should be one of the options that you must consider. All you need to do is properly place them with the help of mouldings or valances. As cove lights are available in various shapes and sizes, you can rest assured that they will create a luxe vibe around your space.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>On that note, take a look at a few of the must-have cove lighting options.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Simple Cove Lighting<\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Grant a luxurious touch to your home with the subtle and muted effect of a string of lights. When strategically placed, this false ceiling cove light design helps in drawing attention just to the right elements of your space.\u00a0 At the same time, they create a warm, cosy effect that uplifts the ambience of your home.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" class=\"wp-image-19044\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204412\/simple-false-ceiling-cove-light.jpg\" alt=\"Simple false ceiling cove light in the living room looks cosy.\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204412\/simple-false-ceiling-cove-light.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204412\/simple-false-ceiling-cove-light-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204412\/simple-false-ceiling-cove-light-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204412\/simple-false-ceiling-cove-light-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/>\r\n<figcaption>Place an array of lights in panels or spread them simply to illuminate your home<\/figcaption>\r\n<\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Cove Lighting<\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Layered lighting is trending these days. Make the most of it by aligning panels and spreading out the lights across your space. Depending upon the size of your home, modern false ceiling cove light design perfectly works for your living room or master bedroom.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" class=\"wp-image-19043\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204405\/modern-cove-light-ceiling.jpg\" alt=\"The white living room has a layered modern cove light ceiling.\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204405\/modern-cove-light-ceiling.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204405\/modern-cove-light-ceiling-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204405\/modern-cove-light-ceiling-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204405\/modern-cove-light-ceiling-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/>\r\n<figcaption>Diffused yet not entirely soft, a modern cove light design always strikes a balance<\/figcaption>\r\n<\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Minimal Cove Lighting<\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Let your living room express itself with this elegant cove light design. Designed keeping your love for minimalism in mind, this design layers up a sequence of lights to grant a halo effect to your space. Include this design in your plan to create a truly luxe, inviting living room.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" class=\"wp-image-19042\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204359\/minimal-led-strip-light-coving.jpg\" alt=\"Living room ceiling with cove light strip, look minimal.\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204359\/minimal-led-strip-light-coving.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204359\/minimal-led-strip-light-coving-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204359\/minimal-led-strip-light-coving-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204359\/minimal-led-strip-light-coving-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/>\r\n<figcaption>Need a layered lighting design? Go for minimal cove lights!<\/figcaption>\r\n<\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Elegant Cove Lighting<\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>While cove lighting without a doubt needs to be functional, we cannot deny its role in adding more sheen to your space.\u00a0 If you agree, then consider choosing cove lights that fit well in wooden panels or intricate engravings that you wish to align in your false ceiling. This design helps in creating aesthetic harmony and looks uber plush. You could choose them for your foyer, living room or dining area to draw attention to the right places.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" class=\"wp-image-19041\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204352\/elegant-led-cove-lighting.jpg\" alt=\"Led cove lighting fitted in a wooden panel in the living cum dining area with an elegant look.\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204352\/elegant-led-cove-lighting.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204352\/elegant-led-cove-lighting-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204352\/elegant-led-cove-lighting-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204352\/elegant-led-cove-lighting-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/>\r\n<figcaption>Grant a plush edge to your space with these sophisticated cove lights<\/figcaption>\r\n<\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Contemporary Cove Lighting<\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Got a guest area, foyer or a section in your bedroom that needs a highlight? Well, you could easily do that by placing an indirect lighting source. It is easily aligned in a false ceiling. This cove light design is timeless. Recreating the delicate, fuzzy vibe in your room is something you will thank yourself for. Play host to your guests, churn up conversations and more with this cove light design helping you with all of it!<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" class=\"wp-image-19039\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204337\/contemporary-cove-light-strip.jpg\" alt=\"The contemporary living room has led strip light coving in the false ceiling corners.\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204337\/contemporary-cove-light-strip.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204337\/contemporary-cove-light-strip-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204337\/contemporary-cove-light-strip-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204337\/contemporary-cove-light-strip-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/>\r\n<figcaption>Create a pacifying nook in your home using contemporary cove lights<\/figcaption>\r\n<\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Classy Cove Lighting<\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Always wanted to make a statement in your space using lights? Well, this design gives you that chance. Intricately designed in a geometric, future-ready way, this cove light design makes your home look more dynamic. You could choose a fluorescent or warm tone of lights as the mood you wish to evoke in your home. This design works well for a living room or even a master bedroom. You could also place it over your dining hall.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" class=\"wp-image-19038\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204331\/classy-cove-light-design.jpg\" alt=\"Classy cove light design in the living room makes the home look more dynamic.\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204331\/classy-cove-light-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204331\/classy-cove-light-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204331\/classy-cove-light-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/10204331\/classy-cove-light-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/>\r\n<figcaption>Let your home be more zestful with this luxe, sleek cove light design<\/figcaption>\r\n<\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>There are indeed a zillion ways in which you could transform your home. But take our word for it: cove lights will help you do that in an instant. Pick your favourite design from our highly recommended line-up for the same or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">reach out to us<\/a> to design custom cove lights of your choice.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Explore, more about<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\r\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/home-lightings-and-its-benefits\/\">Home Lighting And Its Benefits<\/a><\/li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/8-lighting-ideas-for-your-home\/\">8 Lighting Ideas For Your Home<\/a><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06164015\/91.png\"\n                    selected>\n                    +91\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+44\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163955\/44.png\">\n                    +44\n                <\/op